channel.title: == Auxy Forum Awards 2018 — Winners! ==
channel.description:
# Auxy Forum Awards 2018 Winners
The [results](https://disco.auxy.co/t/auxy-forum-awards-2018/) are in! Let's see who the top voted nominees are for the 2018 Auxy Forum Awards...
# BEST AUXY TRACK OF 2018
> **WINNER :unicorn:: <ins>Kevinhood by Kayasho</ins> - [Listen Now] (https://soundcloud.com/kayashokayasho/kevinhood-ep-2-kevinhood)** > 2 :unicorn:. Odyssey by blackocean and Phluze - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/blckocean/blackocean-phluze-odyssey) > 3 :unicorn:. Anti-Edo by Thrashie - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/xkmusickroxiejra/k-ro-anti-edo) > 4th Equal. Essence by Trey - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/treyauxy/essence) > 4th Equal. Orion by Produk and Zeph - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/produkmusic/produk-zeph-orion)
# BEST AUXY PRODUCER OF 2018
> **WINNER :unicorn:: <ins>Kayasho</ins>** > 2nd Equal :unicorn:: NotMiles > 2nd Equal :unicorn:: stereofld > 3. Thrashie > 4. Austin Haga
# MOST INNOVATIVE AUXY TRACK OF 2018
> **WINNER :unicorn:: <ins>198X by Kayasho</ins> - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/kayashokayasho/198x)** > 2. Mothership by IVO and Xiejra - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/xaviormusic/ivo-x-xiejra-mothership) > 3. Viiper by NotMiles - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/not_miles/viiper) > 4. Sherforest by Kayasho - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/kayashokayasho/kevinhood-ep-3-sharforest) > 5. Ripple by ToxicCaves64 - [Listen Now](https://soundcloud.com/wearefrontier/ripple)
# MOST UNIQUE AUXY PRODUCER OF 2018
> **WINNER :unicorn:: <ins>NotMiles</ins>** > 2. Kayasho > 3. Thrashie > 4th Equal: Anechoik > 4th Equal: Cornea
# MOST SUPPORTIVE AUXY PRODUCER OF 2018
> **WINNER :unicorn:: <ins>Mr_Mooo</ins>** > 2 :unicorn:. Hum4n01d > 3rd Equal :unicorn:: Arimyth > 3rd Equal :unicorn:: Hexx > 4. MrSerpent
Congratulations to all of the winners. Winners of the highly sought out and exclusive Unicorns will be noted next to their placing in each category, as well as the appropriate tracks / producers being promoted in the official Auxy App Feed.
Many thanks to everyone for contributing to such a unique and positive community for everyone, and for nominating / voting on this year's forum awards.
Special thanks to our Janitors @MisterMaster and @iammane for keeping the place nice and tidy, and for @Auxy and @Fredrik for continuing to push the boundaries of what's possible with the app they've created.
That's all for now. 'Tis been a pleasure hosting this year's Auxy Forum Awards--here's to a continued great new year and I look forward to seeing all of you develop and continue to create more tracks in the coming year.
